<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٠- كَلَّا إِذا دُكَّتِ الْأَرْضُ دَكًّا دَكًّا <span class="c2">(٢١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَجاءَ رَبُّكَ وَالْمَلَكُ صَفًّا صَفًّا <span class="c2">(٢٢)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَجِيءَ يَوْمَئِذٍ بِجَهَنَّمَ يَوْمَئِذٍ يَتَذَكَّرُ الْإِنْسانُ وَأَنَّى لَهُ الذِّكْرى <span class="c2">(٢٣)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يَقُولُ يا لَيْتَنِي قَدَّمْتُ لِحَياتِي <span class="c2">(٢٤)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَيَوْمَئِذٍ لا يُعَذِّبُ عَذابَهُ أَحَدٌ <span class="c2">(٢٥)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلا يُوثِقُ وَثاقَهُ أَحَدٌ <span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٧١- فَأَنْذَرْتُكُمْ ناراً تَلَظَّى <span class="c2">(١٤)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>لا يَصْلاها إِلَّا الْأَشْقَى <span class="c2">(١٥)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>الَّذِي كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّى <span class="c2">(١٦)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٧٢- وَأَمَّا مَنْ خَفَّتْ مَوازِينُهُ <span class="c2">(٨)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَأُمُّهُ هاوِيَةٌ <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَما أَدْراكَ ما هِيَهْ <span class="c2">(١٠)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>نارٌ حامِيَةٌ <span class="c2">(١١)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٧٣- وَيْلٌ لِكُلِّ هُمَزَةٍ لُمَزَةٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>الَّذِي جَمَعَ مالًا وَعَدَّدَهُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>يَحْسَبُ أَنَّ مالَهُ أَخْلَدَهُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>كَلَّا لَيُنْبَذَنَّ فِي الْحُطَمَةِ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَما أَدْراكَ مَا الْحُطَمَةُ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>نارُ اللَّهِ الْمُوقَدَةُ <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>الَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى الْأَفْئِدَةِ <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>إِنَّها عَلَيْهِمْ مُؤْصَدَةٌ <span class="c2">(٨)</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>فِي عَمَدٍ مُمَدَّدَةٍ <span class="c2">(٩)</span> <span class="c2">«٤»</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>٧٤- فَوَيْلٌ لِلْمُصَلِّينَ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>الَّذِينَ هُمْ عَنْ صَلاتِهِمْ ساهُونَ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>الَّذِينَ هُمْ يُراؤُنَ <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>وَيَمْنَعُونَ الْماعُونَ <span class="c2">(٧)</span> <span class="c2">«٥»</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
